    <entry>
      <title>使用Valine给Hexo主题添加评论模块,解决评论无法提交的问题</title>
      <link href="/2022/07/20/shi-yong-valine-gei-hexo-zhu-ti-tian-jia-ping-lun-mo-kuai-jie-jue-ping-lun-wu-fa-ti-jiao-de-wen-ti/"/>
      <url>/2022/07/20/shi-yong-valine-gei-hexo-zhu-ti-tian-jia-ping-lun-mo-kuai-jie-jue-ping-lun-wu-fa-ti-jiao-de-wen-ti/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="介绍-Valine-一款快速、简洁且高效的无后端评论系统。"><a href="#介绍-Valine-一款快速、简洁且高效的无后端评论系统。" class="headerlink" title="介绍 | Valine 一款快速、简洁且高效的无后端评论系统。"></a>介绍 | Valine 一款快速、简洁且高效的无后端评论系统。</h2><p><a href="https://valine.js.org/">https://valine.js.org/</a>      </p><h2 id="LeanCloud"><a href="#LeanCloud" class="headerlink" title="LeanCloud"></a>LeanCloud</h2><p><a href="https://console.leancloud.app/apps">https://console.leancloud.app/apps</a>        </p><p>TIP:如果有这个需要，可以将 artitalk 与 valine 存放在同一个应用中。可以有效避免同一个页面使用两个leancloud应用所产生的冲突。     </p><p>我的hexo主题安装在D:\Blog路径下。       </p><p>由于我之前已经使用artitalk.js实现了说说模块，所以我接下来的操作都在当时创建的应用上进行。使用Artitalk为Hexo添加说说模块 | Sammie<br><a href="https://isammiei.github.io/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/">https://isammiei.github.io/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/</a>       </p><p>登录LeanCloud国际版，打开应用，在结构化数据中创建 class，命名为 Comment。      </p><img src="/2022/07/20/shi-yong-valine-gei-hexo-zhu-ti-tian-jia-ping-lun-mo-kuai-jie-jue-ping-lun-wu-fa-ti-jiao-de-wen-ti/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png" class="">       <p>编辑matery主题的配置文件_config.yml中，修改Valine属性：<br>（我的文件在D:\Blog\themes\matery路径下）       </p><img src="/2022/07/20/shi-yong-valine-gei-hexo-zhu-ti-tian-jia-ping-lun-mo-kuai-jie-jue-ping-lun-wu-fa-ti-jiao-de-wen-ti/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.png" class="">       <p>找到js:开头的代码块，找到valine属性，将其修改为     </p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">valine: https://unpkg.com/valine/dist/Valine.min.js      <span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><img src="/2022/07/20/shi-yong-valine-gei-hexo-zhu-ti-tian-jia-ping-lun-mo-kuai-jie-jue-ping-lun-wu-fa-ti-jiao-de-wen-ti/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873.png" class="">       <p>在D盘，选中Blog文件夹，右键，选择Git Bush Here，输入以下命令查看效果<code>hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</code>出现如下页面        </p><img src="/2022/07/20/shi-yong-valine-gei-hexo-zhu-ti-tian-jia-ping-lun-mo-kuai-jie-jue-ping-lun-wu-fa-ti-jiao-de-wen-ti/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%874.png" class="">       <p>但我到了此步，出现了一个问题，评论无法提交！        </p><p>参考了这篇文章，解决了问题      </p><p>【解决方法】Valine评论不显示_靖待的博客-CSDN博客        </p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/hubojing/article/details/121770387">https://blog.csdn.net/hubojing/article/details/121770387</a>      </p><p>如果主题中已配置的Valine有severURLs字段，直接设置即可。比如在D:\Blog\themes\matery路径下的_config.yml文件中     </p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">serverURLs: https://xxxxxxxx.api.lncldglobal.com # 把xxxxxxxx替换为自己AppID的前8位字符<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><img src="/2022/07/20/shi-yong-valine-gei-hexo-zhu-ti-tian-jia-ping-lun-mo-kuai-jie-jue-ping-lun-wu-fa-ti-jiao-de-wen-ti/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%875.png" class="">       <p>如果主题中已配置的Valine没有severURLs字段，找到valine的js文件，增加一行代码，       </p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">serverURLs: '&lt;%= theme.valine.serverURLs %&gt;'  // 增加这一行！！！<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>      <p>比如我的在D:\Blog\themes\matery\layout_partial路径下的valine.ejs       </p><p>把<code>&lt;script src="//cdn1.lncld.net/static/js/3.0.4/av-min.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;      </code></p><p>替换成</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">&lt;script src="&lt;%- theme.jsDelivr.url %&gt;&lt;%- url_for('/libs/valine/av-min.js') %&gt;"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>      <img src="/2022/07/20/shi-yong-valine-gei-hexo-zhu-ti-tian-jia-ping-lun-mo-kuai-jie-jue-ping-lun-wu-fa-ti-jiao-de-wen-ti/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%876.png" class="">   <p>在D盘，选中Blog文件夹，右键，选择Git Bush Here，输入命令<code>hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</code>出现以下页面，评论可以成功提交了！      </p><img src="/2022/07/20/shi-yong-valine-gei-hexo-zhu-ti-tian-jia-ping-lun-mo-kuai-jie-jue-ping-lun-wu-fa-ti-jiao-de-wen-ti/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%877.png" class="">   <p>最后，输入命令<code>hexo cl &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</code>发布</p>]]></content>
      
      
