      <title>使用Artitalk为Hexo添加说说模块</title>
      <link href="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/"/>
      <url>/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="hexo使用文档-Artitalk-js"><a href="#hexo使用文档-Artitalk-js" class="headerlink" title="hexo使用文档 | Artitalk.js"></a>hexo使用文档 | Artitalk.js</h2><p><a href="https://artitalk.js.org/doc.html#%F0%9F%91%80-%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80">https://artitalk.js.org/doc.html#%F0%9F%91%80-%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80</a>      </p><h2 id="LeanCloud-的相关准备"><a href="#LeanCloud-的相关准备" class="headerlink" title="LeanCloud 的相关准备"></a>LeanCloud 的相关准备</h2><ol><li><p>前往 LeanCloud 国际版，注册账号。<a href="https://console.leancloud.app/apps">https://console.leancloud.app/apps</a>     </p></li><li><p>注册完成之后根据 LeanCloud 的提示绑定手机号和邮箱。<br>绑定完成之后点击创建应用，应用名称随意，</p></li></ol><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png" class=""><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.png" class=""><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873.png" class=""><ol start="3"><li>接着在结构化数据中创建 class，命名为 shuoshuo。</li></ol><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%874.png" class=""><ol start="4"><li>在你新建的应用中找到结构化数据下的用户。点击添加用户，输入想用的用户名及密码。</li></ol><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%875.png" class=""><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%876.png" class=""><ol start="5"><li>回到结构化数据中，点击 class 下的 shuoshuo。找到权限，在 Class 访问权限中将 add_fields 以及 create 权限设置为指定用户，输入你刚才输入的用户名会自动匹配。为了安全起见，将 delete 和 update 也设置为跟它们一样的权限。</li></ol><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%877.png" class=""><ol start="6"><li>然后新建一个名为atComment的class，权限什么的使用默认的即可。</li></ol><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%878.png" class=""><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%879.png" class=""><ol start="7"><li>点击 class 下的 _User 添加列，列名称为 img，默认值填上你这个账号想要用的发布说说的头像url，这一项不进行配置，说说头像会显示为默认头像 —— Artitalk 的 logo。</li></ol><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8710.png" class=""><ol start="8"><li>在最菜单栏中找到设置-&gt; 应用 keys，记下来 AppID 和 AppKey ，一会会用。</li></ol><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8711.png" class=""><ol start="9"><li>最后将 _User 中的权限全部调为指定用户，或者数据创建者，为了保证不被篡改用户数据以达到强制发布说说。</li></ol><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8712.png" class=""><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8713.png" class=""><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8714.png" class=""><p>❗ 关于设置权限的这几步     </p><p>这几步一定要设置好，才可以保证不被 “闲人” 破解发布说说的验证</p><h2 id="开始使用"><a href="#开始使用" class="headerlink" title="开始使用"></a>开始使用</h2><p>我的Hexo安装在D:\Blog路径下，接下来的步骤按照你所安装的位置来操作。     </p><p>在D盘，选中Blog文件夹，右键，选择Git Bush Here      </p><p>如果在你的博客 source 目录下还没有 artitalk.md 文件，那么你就需要新建一个</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo new page artitalk      <span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8715.png" class=""><p>编辑你刚刚新建的页面文件 /source/artitalk/index.md，至少需要以下内容：      </p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">---title: artitalkdate: 2022-07-17 14:10:10type: artitalklayout: 'artitalk'---<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8716.png" class=""><p>在D:\Blog\themes\matery\layout路径下新建一个artitalk.ejs文件，编辑文件，至少需要以下内容：      </p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">&lt;%- partial('_partial/bg-cover') %&gt;&lt;!-- 引用 artitalk --&gt;&lt;script type="text/javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/artitalk"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;!-- 存放说说的容器 --&gt;&lt;div id="artitalk_main"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;script&gt;new Artitalk({    appId: '', // Your LeanCloud appId    appKey: '' // Your LeanCloud appKey})&lt;/script&gt;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8717.png" class=""><p>编辑D:\Blog\themes\matery路径下的_config.yml文件，配置菜单导航的名称、路径和图标，内容如下      </p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">Artitalk:    url: /artitalkicon: fas fa-comment<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8718.png" class=""><p>在D盘，选中Blog文件夹，右键，选择Git Bush Here，先不更新部署，输入以下命令查看效果      </p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>      <p>出现如下页面         </p><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8719.png" class=""><p>登录账号        </p><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720.png" class=""><p>这是发布说说的效果      </p><img src="/2022/07/18/shi-yong-artitalk-wei-hexo-tian-jia-shuo-shuo-mo-kuai/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8721.png" class=""><p>如果做到这一步，那说明成功了，最后，输入命令发布        </p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo cl &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
